<node id="RFP Section J-L">
  <data key="d0">RFP Section J-L</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">RFP Sections J-L contain specific instructions and attachments for contractors.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP Section J-L is a section of an RFP document.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP Section J-L pertains to attachments JL-1 Staffing Levels.&lt;SEP&gt;Section J-L pertains to attachments related to the total effort including prime contractor and subcontractors for the base period.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP Sections J-L provide details on staffing levels and management approach evaluation factors.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP Section J-L refers to sections in a request for proposal document.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP Section J-L is a section of the Request for Proposal document.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a3fc5d0a3c062b2644322e5f456a949c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5f0e0608ea19b134885b11b9c0109bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ddf9c5f78a57f5d83cb20887f8824a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65dfa974c1d7fde3efddd161f2d0c111&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61694aa1368ed858ad8df606fa04c252&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbeaa1c5ef8881ecb29238efcfb04044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d711dadff4a453395afe47e66633011</data>
