<node id="Attachment L">
  <data key="d0">Attachment L</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Attachment L is a part of RFP Section J-L, containing notices and special instructions.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment L is part of the RFP document.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment L is one of the required documents for the RFP Section J-L, detailing the total effort including prime contractor and all subcontractors for the base period.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment L contains requirements for BOEs and methodology descriptions.&lt;SEP&gt;Attachment L is part of the RFP document containing specific requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a3fc5d0a3c062b2644322e5f456a949c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5f0e0608ea19b134885b11b9c0109bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65dfa974c1d7fde3efddd161f2d0c111&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61694aa1368ed858ad8df606fa04c252&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbeaa1c5ef8881ecb29238efcfb04044</data>
