<node id="RFP Section J-Line">
  <data key="d0">RFP Section J-Line</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">RFP Section J-Line, also known as J-line, is a specific section within Request For Proposal (RFP) documents. It pertains to attachment line details and pricing submission format for End Item Numbers (ELINs) Spreadsheet. This section is part of the acquisition process related to attachment lines and serves as an event for submitting attachments and ELINs spreadsheet. RFP Section J-Line does not explicitly refer to a specific event, but rather a section within the RFP document outlining requirements for attachment line submission.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba40693e44188c0b7135805bafc948b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec609ec9d15dc5a326c45c679863f016&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa5ea3a28222b8648eab5c03cb03259b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67e7d5a4eb966e5441d36cef24252be2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfe486f2bce440b90e1432824fd8df7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06ec2afb447854579c9ed8aef5e4ae44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6263b51ad0b94a028bc661541aa9bc1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-028d951e6ae4a814225f26ebc56dc025&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b381aaf8ac346e0f574c2e78a1b9a4c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e590ed6cd5325a2a39bf136ed26a6ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ee5ae2c7877f3dacda1fd41c4003706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd47b80d73108183223aee35fa6a5bef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a49b3fca27d1bfcbacc4e065fbe60b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-093501964c34aac26cd43b1fee022a61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf1db416b2122957c36ecbee38f3fe31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10f1ab31f15793d6883ed16e49cb47a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4669cec0beac695d21e676ca63d73fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-862cc61a82688524670be7932970db34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-becee7385eea241e5f474e2149cdabc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-332f1e0210c1bb98df9727bae4154691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6add693625a796a1a81529e7908d9d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53c87f8fb64940738805e7738f81d145&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5969ddb56b77ea121b633c84fa35a1cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e153ceb6e5974b3c468ca0e28c12f17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63132a97aa785239c072e22506fb4ea7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4b2348a15a936a501a1844d3d6ba3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dab14612198fb4b5d462c84dfda8857c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84b8afe3d224d51ffef3c4452d53d12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea390bb5aa0246491e8a1d9442de8ce2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e101b73a5b1a950d1879f4b36cb7dc9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a8d2d7e6059bb205824dfeac13f31f5</data>
