  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">"J-0200000-17 ELINs.xlsx is a Microsoft Excel spreadsheet file containing electronic library information numbers (ELINs) and corresponding item numbers. It is specifically related to the RFP Section J-Line attachment line. This data file serves as an important reference for items associated with this section of the Request For Proposal (RFP)."</data>
