<node id="Attachment Line">
  <data key="d0">Attachment Line</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">**Attachment Line**

An Attachment Line is a specific line item associated with Exhibit Line Item Numbers (ELINs), signifying the exact location within an attachment where detailed items are listed. It represents a line in an attachment of a Request For Proposal (RFP), relating to specific item numbers and sub-item numbers, and providing additional pricing details and guidelines as part of the RFP Section J-Line. The Attachment Line is not an attachment itself but rather a component within the RFP document that facilitates the organization and clarity of attachment information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5969ddb56b77ea121b633c84fa35a1cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4b2348a15a936a501a1844d3d6ba3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63132a97aa785239c072e22506fb4ea7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-093501964c34aac26cd43b1fee022a61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-862cc61a82688524670be7932970db34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd47b80d73108183223aee35fa6a5bef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-028d951e6ae4a814225f26ebc56dc025&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84b8afe3d224d51ffef3c4452d53d12f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec609ec9d15dc5a326c45c679863f016&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67e7d5a4eb966e5441d36cef24252be2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea390bb5aa0246491e8a1d9442de8ce2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06ec2afb447854579c9ed8aef5e4ae44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e101b73a5b1a950d1879f4b36cb7dc9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a8d2d7e6059bb205824dfeac13f31f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6add693625a796a1a81529e7908d9d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf1db416b2122957c36ecbee38f3fe31</data>
