  <data key="d0">Exhibit Line Item</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Exhibit Line Item represents a type of line item in relation to ELINs.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit Line Item represents the display or presentation of line item information.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit Line Item pertains to a list or table within an exhibit of the RFP document.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit Line Item refers to the line items displayed in an exhibit, likely within a Request For Proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;An Exhibit Line Item refers to individual entries listed under specific exhibits, typically within a Request for Proposal (RFP) document.&lt;SEP&gt;An exhibit line item in the RFP document.</data>
