<node id="RFP">
  <data key="d0">RFP</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">RFP refers to Request For Proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP is a request for proposal document used by the Government to solicit offers from potential contractors.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP refers to a Request For Proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP refers to the Request for Proposal document used in procurement processes.&lt;SEP&gt;The RFP provides guidelines for staffing levels and evaluation factors.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP is a Request For Proposal document that outlines requirements for contractors.&lt;SEP&gt;RFP represents a request for proposal in the provided context.</data>
