<node id="MCSF-BI">
  <data key="d0">MCSF-BI</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">**Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island (MCSF-BI)**

MCSF-BI, located in Jacksonville, Florida, is a Marine Corps Support Facility that serves as a hub for various facilities management services. Primarily known for its facilities inventory services, MCSF-BI also provides compressed air systems and is involved with custodial services, including pest control.

The facility is associated with several infrastructure components:

- **Irrigation Systems**: MCSF-BI manages irrigation equipment and systems inventory.
- **Lighting Systems**: The organization is involved with lighting systems maintenance and management.
- **Lift Stations**: MCSF-BI oversees lift stations related to water treatment and distribution.
- **Portable Toilets &amp; Sewage Holding Tanks**: The facility manages portable toilet services and appears to be associated with sewage holding tanks.
- **Fuel Storage Tanks**: MCSF-BI handles fuel storage tank inventory and custodial services.

Additionally, MCSF-BI is involved in:

- **Stormwater Management**: The organization works on stormwater pollution prevention plans and is mentioned in relation to stormwater system maps and Environmental Laboratory Information Networks (ELINs).
- **Shoreline Cleanup Activities**: MCSF-BI participates in shoreline cleanup efforts.
- **Maps &amp; Plans**: The facility provides various maps such as Blount Island Site Map, Facility Investment maps, roadway and parking lot maps (J-1503050-09 Paved Roadways &amp; Lots Map.pdf), and custodial maps.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fa5ea3a28222b8648eab5c03cb03259b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06ec2afb447854579c9ed8aef5e4ae44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbeaa1c5ef8881ecb29238efcfb04044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b942599f79f358c4b8d64bfbb16dd0d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ee5ae2c7877f3dacda1fd41c4003706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-074a503b39aab6c1b3875bb79c4a1177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a6ecf1e45deea680418315d44951ff3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d320b5bd6d2d86c2678f2811bf8a0cc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f5f2004366fb743afcc4d076fe18de1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd1bc423a94fbff0f5c64122ba7746cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27a9a8b0d81d4985cf2d06ddde56336a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-862cc61a82688524670be7932970db34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3415746feff51039d7e1a889c5b0cf7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6add693625a796a1a81529e7908d9d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e153ceb6e5974b3c468ca0e28c12f17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4b2348a15a936a501a1844d3d6ba3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63132a97aa785239c072e22506fb4ea7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ad24903a4dbf56baa7a5fb8317a2098&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b7143ec2bc14930f4dd7cb3b5cf1e35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea390bb5aa0246491e8a1d9442de8ce2</data>
