<node id="Government">
  <data key="d0">Government</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Government is the entity with which the contract is made.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is the entity responsible for making awards, including transition periods.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is the entity overseeing and paying for the contract performance.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is the entity responsible for evaluating offers and rounding unit prices if necessary.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is the entity responsible for evaluating offers and awarding contracts based on the best value proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is evaluating offerors' management approaches for a project.&lt;SEP&gt;The Government is the entity responsible for providing acquisition opportunities and assessing small business utilization.</data>
