<node id="Attachment J-0200000-17">
  <data key="d0">Attachment J-0200000-17</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Attachment J-0200000-17 is an attachment to the Request for Proposal (RFP), specifically tied to RFP Section J-0200000. It is referenced in various sections of the RFP, including CLIN 0013, Option Line Item 0015, CLIN 0016, CLIN 0022, CLIN 0023, and CLIN 0027. This attachment serves as a worksheet tab for these contract line item numbers (CLINs), containing pricing arrangement details and specific requirements related to the RFP sections mentioned above.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0032ac1505bc8aa343a800ceff232e28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa57ec53441fc345ab04930192023a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fabc9338ccf03d7c1292113c4897c7c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c3606c8f7b2964d3495f85a1fdd465b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ce2548337b8b7064fd3aa28ee4dd105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6719179bf5c40133993a200b8315ec33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44cf85dec0fec59361aa3b5e47811250&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a418b0b9381e31b88a60c9b5bb63e77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04a2b8ffa2a50c16761439fbed0b449c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b18ef2c7868c3b985a84d175422535dd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759451529</data>
</node>
<node id="Performance Work Statement">
  <data key="d0">Performance Work Statement</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">A Performance Work Statement (PWS) is a critical document that comprehensively outlines the expected outcomes, deliverables, tasks, and services for a project or contract. It serves as a reference point throughout the procurement process, including for pricing arrangements (e.g., CLIN 0017, CLIN 0023 7th Period Opt N-RW). The PWS defines detailed requirements for the services or products to be delivered under the contract, encompassing all management and administration requirements, performance objectives, and standards. It is often referenced as an applicable attachment to the contract and provides a comprehensive overview of the work required from offerors within the contract. In some instances, it may specifically define requirements for Recurring Base Operations Support Services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47c5b16ca68b3ce4da8cf59d700a0552&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6f6d7ee5e904366a5f727d9c8e9b5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea26fde1901b2f6713654fee35033196&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d90086a5377424509d24bef348c64624&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6719179bf5c40133993a200b8315ec33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d1afdb404d508b4795d2d97f0a9440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0032ac1505bc8aa343a800ceff232e28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa57ec53441fc345ab04930192023a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-195f0b6d0eb8978e12a550de5227f088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9688477020b78bd66f295fe2e7018cdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e50bf4d58079ccb2c1fb7cb05ca6f201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-205fa026f7c673d73741f92ed24db584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c3606c8f7b2964d3495f85a1fdd465b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ddf9c5f78a57f5d83cb20887f8824a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44cf85dec0fec59361aa3b5e47811250&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8459283e38daefcdf466872389b2a66e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b18ef2c7868c3b985a84d175422535dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0ec534cedde816f134ee4c2df639f3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ce2548337b8b7064fd3aa28ee4dd105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d711dadff4a453395afe47e66633011</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759451540</data>
</node>
<node id="Offeror">
  <data key="d0">Offeror</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Offeror: An Offeror, also referred to as an offeror, is an entity that submits proposals in response to Requests For Proposals (RFPs). In the context of government acquisitions and project work, an offeror can be any potential contractor submitting proposals for evaluation or tendering offers. This includes bidders or proposers who aim to provide services or goods as per the specified requirements of a contract or project.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6a57acefedb0403481c47df8f5eb5e77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2caaa8564fe3944085a1062c6730b7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70c8b4e3fd1f28b4822549ea3b9c8bd3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1547566630303dcf47da116e57ad8978&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ff4e5a9265af4a827117412e6782545&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79878567a06848702be3aef0d2e088cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66f32f434893c4bf82eca92cfe95a02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d711dadff4a453395afe47e66633011&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d71291fb679aa4d9c7e414fc857c490a</data>
