  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">FFP stands for Firm Fixed Price, indicating a pricing arrangement where the total cost of the product or service is agreed upon beforehand and does not change throughout the project lifecycle.&lt;SEP&gt;FFP is an abbreviation for Firm Fixed Price.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c9d1afdb404d508b4795d2d97f0a9440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9</data>
