<node id="Recurring Base Operations Support Services">
  <data key="d0">Recurring Base Operations Support Services</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Recurring Base Operations Support Services is a type of service that provides ongoing assistance with operations and maintenance tasks, charged on a recurring basis.&lt;SEP&gt;Recurring Base Operations Support Services involve regular, ongoing support services.&lt;SEP&gt;Recurring Base Operations Support Services is a type of support service offered under the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;A type of support service provided under the contract&lt;SEP&gt;Recurring Base Operations Support Services are ongoing services provided by contractors to support the operations of an organization.&lt;SEP&gt;Recurring Base Operations Support Services are services provided under the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Recurring Base Operations Support Services are routine tasks performed under the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47c5b16ca68b3ce4da8cf59d700a0552&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e50bf4d58079ccb2c1fb7cb05ca6f201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-195f0b6d0eb8978e12a550de5227f088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea26fde1901b2f6713654fee35033196&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d1afdb404d508b4795d2d97f0a9440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1</data>
