<node id="RFP Section J-0200000">
  <data key="d0">RFP Section J-0200000</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">**RFP Section J-0200000** is a section within Request for Proposal (RFP) documents, specifically dedicated to attachments. This section is associated with Attachment 0200000 and contains pricing arrangements and support services details. It serves as the location where this attachment is situated in the RFP document. As part of its contents, offerors are required to submit exhibit line item numbers for consideration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47c5b16ca68b3ce4da8cf59d700a0552&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a65e507c3cadde9b847528f2bfcba271&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6f6d7ee5e904366a5f727d9c8e9b5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea26fde1901b2f6713654fee35033196&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d7965b8179327e4a7b17022a313ac8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d1afdb404d508b4795d2d97f0a9440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04a2b8ffa2a50c16761439fbed0b449c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0032ac1505bc8aa343a800ceff232e28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa57ec53441fc345ab04930192023a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-195f0b6d0eb8978e12a550de5227f088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9688477020b78bd66f295fe2e7018cdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e50bf4d58079ccb2c1fb7cb05ca6f201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1134bde47b2e4250302b40f0cd197b50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-205fa026f7c673d73741f92ed24db584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6452d63d89da4803c08bf42cdbc18f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44cf85dec0fec59361aa3b5e47811250&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8459283e38daefcdf466872389b2a66e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-115aaf08f9d88c27dbec90f0bcea3f22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fabc9338ccf03d7c1292113c4897c7c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0ec534cedde816f134ee4c2df639f3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ce2548337b8b7064fd3aa28ee4dd105</data>
