<node id="Option Line Item">
  <data key="d0">Option Line Item</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Option Line Item is a category of line items found in contracts or RFPs, specifically referring to optional elements or services. These options are priced separately and allow for additional features or services to be added at an extra cost under certain conditions or periods, such as those within Option Period 1 Recurring - Water Annex. As a type of line item in the pricing arrangement, it provides flexibility by enabling entities to elect specific optional elements, thus representing an option that can be exercised under defined circumstances.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0032ac1505bc8aa343a800ceff232e28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e50bf4d58079ccb2c1fb7cb05ca6f201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a65e507c3cadde9b847528f2bfcba271&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6f6d7ee5e904366a5f727d9c8e9b5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea26fde1901b2f6713654fee35033196&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0ec534cedde816f134ee4c2df639f3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1</data>
