<edge source="RFP Section J-0200000" target="Attachment 0200000">
  <data key="d6">16.0</data>
  <data key="d7">The relation named "(Attachment 0200000, RFP Section J-0200000)" concerns the association between an attachment and its corresponding section in a Request for Proposal (RFP). This relation is consistently described across multiple sources, with no conflicts or inconsistencies. The attachment, numbered 0200000, is closely associated with RFP Section J-0200000. It appears that the attachment is included within or attached to the specified RFP section, and vice versa, indicating a reciprocal relationship between these two entities.</data>
  <data key="d8">attachment,attachment reference,containment,contains,contractual relationship,document composition,document hierarchy,document relationship,document section,document sections,document structure,document_attachment,reference,refers to,relationship,section relation</data>
  <data key="d9">chunk-47c5b16ca68b3ce4da8cf59d700a0552&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e50bf4d58079ccb2c1fb7cb05ca6f201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1134bde47b2e4250302b40f0cd197b50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6f6d7ee5e904366a5f727d9c8e9b5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6452d63d89da4803c08bf42cdbc18f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-195f0b6d0eb8978e12a550de5227f088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea26fde1901b2f6713654fee35033196&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a65e507c3cadde9b847528f2bfcba271&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88ec1d25f6b9d47e8bbd18881f0734e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0ec534cedde816f134ee4c2df639f3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ce2548337b8b7064fd3aa28ee4dd105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9d1afdb404d508b4795d2d97f0a9440&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8459283e38daefcdf466872389b2a66e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9688477020b78bd66f295fe2e7018cdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61cd65d989970185b729effedefbd4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04a2b8ffa2a50c16761439fbed0b449c</data>
